# Project Context

This is a personal portfolio website built with Next.js 15, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Velite (Content management)
- shadcn/ui (Components)
- Biome (Linting & Formatting)

## Code Style
- Use functional components with TypeScript
- Use Tailwind for styling (no CSS modules)
- Use server components by default, client components only when needed
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions
- Use Biome for linting and formatting

## File Naming
- Components: PascalCase (e.g., BlogCard.tsx)
- Utils: camelCase (e.g., formatDate.ts)
- Pages: lowercase (e.g., page.tsx)
- Config files: lowercase with dashes (e.g., site-config.ts)

## Component Structure
- Export component as named export
- Include JSDoc comments for complex components
- Use TypeScript interfaces for props
- Props interface should be named ComponentNameProps

## Content
- Blog posts in content/blog/*.mdx
- Projects in content/projects/*.mdx
- Use frontmatter for metadata
- Velite will generate type-safe content

## Styling
- Use Tailwind utility classes
- Use CSS variables for theming
- Support dark mode with next-themes
- Follow shadcn/ui patterns

## Imports
- Use @ alias for src imports
- Group imports: external, internal, relative
- Use named exports over default exports
